@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_revhex(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = ((v0 - (tmp + 0.33 + v0 + 0.86)) / wp.abs(tmp))
    v0 = 0.37
    tmp = ((wp.cos(v0 + 0.73) / v1) + (tmp + wp.exp(v2 + 0.06)))
    v0 = 0.18
    data[tid] = v0
